<p><strong>Definition (Exposed Point):</strong> <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?x%20%5Cin%20%5Cmathbb%20R"> is consider an <strong>exposed point</strong> for function <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?f:%20%5Cmathbb%20R%20%5Cto%20%5Cmathbb%20R">, if <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cexists%20t"> s.t. <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cforall%20y%20%5Cneq%20x"> the following holds <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cbegin%7Balign%7D%0A%20%20t%20y%20-%20f(y)%20%3E%20t%20x%20-%20f(x)%0A%5Cend%7Balign%7D"></p>



